title: Temporary need for EM coverage in NY for an ED with less than 25K annual vo... at Locumtenens.com (New York)
text: Source: LocumTenens.com Temporary need for EM coverage in NY for an ED with less than 25K annual volume. Admission rate 14%, trauma level III, fast track and hospitalist program on site. Physicians need to have an active NY license and be Board Certified EM, FP, or IM with current ATLS, ACLS, PALS. Start date anticipated to be 60 days from acceptance.
